definition.text: It is the most basic and low level system-wide configuration file. You will find it at the Projects folder. It contains a list of all integrated projects and for each one the list of javascript modules organized in different categories, like Function Libraries, Utilities, Spaces, Globals, etc; in turn organized into the broather categories UI, TS and CL.

paragraphs.text: Left click and Edit to enter edit mode and change this text. ENTER to write new paragraphs. ESC to exit edit mode. Then you can use docs.save to save your changes and app.contribute to send it to the main repository.
